modName: Mount and Blade Warband War Legacy version 0.52
summary: This is a patch version 0.52 for Mount and Blade Warband War Legacy. In added IronMan, and the Dragon Knights.
descriptionHtml: Also added some more armors and weapons. In the next patch I will make sure all armors work together nicely. Also I will add Spiderman, Venom and Phantom in the next patch. Add the new patch into your modules replacing the old version. Also you will have to start a new game if you want to see all the new weapons and armors. Please, dont forget to support me if you want to see more. Thank you! Enjoy!
author: 3DVIZZION
